INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('171', '3', '2', '我办开展学校教学基础设施督查工作', '发规目督办', '超级管理员', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 37px; line-height: 21px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 19px; line-height: 28.5px; font-family: 宋体;\">根据学校本科教学审核评估工作安排，</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 19px; line-height: 28.5px;\">3</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 19px; line-height: 28.5px; font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 19px; line-height: 28.5px;\">21</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 19px; line-height: 28.5px; font-family: 宋体;\">日上午，我办主任周勇会同评建办公室、教务处、学工部、后勤处等单位负责人到美术学院和音乐学院开展教学基础设施督查工作。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 37px; line-height: 21px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 19px; line-height: 28.5px; font-family: 宋体;\">检查组一行逐一查看美术楼和音乐楼中存在的问题，提出了整改意见，责成两个学院尽快形成整改方案上报学校相关部门，抓紧落实整改工作，做好本科教学审核评估准备工作，以良好的精神面貌和美观整洁的环境迎接本科教学工作审核评估专家组的到来。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/upload/ueditor/2017-06-26/fbd5e6f85a4911e78bb80050569a1c03.png\" title=\"109420b10fce11e791c70050569a1c03.png\" alt=\"109420b10fce11e791c70050569a1c03.png\" width=\"686\" height=\"429\" style=\"width: 686px; height: 429px;\"/><br/></p>', '75', '2017-03-23 16:30:19', '2017-06-26 16:32:49', '1');
